reviewText: Was hoping it had Bus CDL dvd
Boyfriend used this to study for his CDL. He does not like to setudy, so I brought this to help him. After watching it a few times, he passed after one try
Film is out dated and of poor quality. don't spend you  money.

This is just what we needed for our little department.
I would recommend this for any department that has new bus drivers coming in.
